{"tid":2095033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平時間：長江源源不斷綠色動力","createTime":"2020-07-05T06:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T02:15:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"022e906584a879465a565bd9739ec6677037b8d5","tid":2095033,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.newsimg.cn/xjp20171103/images/mb_xjp_banner.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsimg.cn%2Fxjp20171103%2Fimages%2Fmb_xjp_banner.jpg&h=ae2b506f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平總書記日前對金沙江烏東德水電站首批機組投産發電作出重要指示，強調要堅持生態優先、綠色發展，科學有序推進金沙江水能資源開發，推動金沙江流域在保護中發展、在發展中保護，更好造福人民。<br />\n<br />\n　　烏東德水電站的投産發電，將為長江經濟帶建設、中國經濟發展提供源源不斷的綠色動力。近年來，長江沿江各地堅持生態優先，推動黃金水道綠色發展，一幅人與自然和諧共處的生態畫卷正在鋪展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/video/2020-07/04/1210687930_15938705598641n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fvideo%2F2020-07%2F04%2F1210687930_15938705598641n.jpg&h=68d00205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://big5.xinhuanet. com/gate/big5/www.xinhuanet.com/video/2020-07/04/c_1210687930.htm</code></pre>"},{"pid":"588672f0f64e4bcbcb1d83e451a7b68be47a180c","tid":2095033,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"人與自然和諧共處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9540ad8e18174a31358410e291b1c8913df3a6","tid":2095033,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"PTT  [爆卦] 上課中的小學生　整班被洪水沖走了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094826</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n源源不斷"},{"pid":"946f16d8af